sub_title: Cardiologist / electrophysiologist at OLVG. MD, PhD, FESC, FEHRA. Waarnemend opleider. Nicknamed 'Idea Factory'.
summary:
Cardiologist & electrophysiologist. Specialized in cardiac arrhythmias, catheterablation of arrhythmias (about 225/year), and (leadless) ICD/CRTD/pacemaker implantations (about 80/year). 
Special interest in education. Founder of ECGpedia and the Cardionetworks Foundation, a non-profit that improves access to medical knowledge.
Scientific interest in catheter ablation, surviving sudden cardiac death and electrocardiography. (Co)authored more than 40 peer reviewed papers. 
Vice Dean of Cardiology at OLVG. Editor of cardiology for NTVG. 
CMO of Happitech.
